{{Quote|When they came upon me, I thought it was curtains for me. They started to grunt at me, holding out some spears and pointing to my artwork. All they kept saying was Janta. Looking back, I think they were trying to trade with me, but I don't know how to communicate with them.|An artisan, to a spacer|<ref name="SWG:ac">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=herald|A commoner|Dantooine}}</ref>}}
'''Dantarian''', also known as '''Dantari''', was the native tongue of the [[Dantari]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. Being simple, primitive nomads, the Dantari were not a learned species. There was a [[Writing/Legends|written form]] of Dantarian, but it was only known by a select few.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

